title: 'If you don't like Australia, leave', Muslim leader to tell Parramatta worshippers
text: The chairman of a Sydney mosque is expected to tell worshippers that " if you don't like Australia, leave " during his first sermon since a teenage extremist who attended the mosque shot dead a civilian police employee. ...
